		<td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/lotr/gfx/mom/whi_08.gif"><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Spokane DPC 1st Place</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><table width='98' border='0' cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'><tr><td background='/lotr/gfx/5star.gif'><img src='/lotr/gfx/trans.gif' width='1' height='25'></td></tr></table><font size=1>(4.91)</font> | <A HREF="/lotr/decks/decks.php?reviews=30217&PHPSESSID=4159d3c40004d8c850f342b7c2ec969b">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=3300">Ryan "Shadow 13" French</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=3300&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> The Fellowship I&#39;ve been playing all year, teamed up with a fairly standard Cave Troll Moria for the ultimate stopping power.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> September 3, 2003</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Frodo OBH<br />
Isildur&#39;s Bane<br />
